<div class="ani-result-summary" id="ani-summary-box">
  <strong>Result:</strong> Assumed Nonimpact skips functions that do not receive tracked values. Calling convention recovery using angr identifies value dependencies per call site. 2 of 4 function calls skipped in this example; at scale, the majority are skipped.
