        Scaling Fuzzing Alone Isn't Enough
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 px-8 md:px-12 py-3 md:py-5 overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center">
        <div class="slide-body">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 1000 320" style="width:100%; margin:0 auto; display:block;" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
